---
title: BBQ Pulled Chicken Sliders with Tangy Cabbage Slaw
description: Southern barbecue is famous for its tangy, vinegar-based sauce, which is then tossed with juicy pulled chicken. This barbecue sauce will have you ditching the bottled kind. A little bit of slaw on the sliders adds the essential 'crunch'!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mini-burgers-au-poulet-effiloche-bbq-80d71287.jpg
